This PR tries to cover most of the functionality the HMW-IO-12-Sw14-DR can provide. The only thing missing would be the analog outputs, for which we don't have suitable controls in HASS anyway.

The configured mode of each relevant channel is checked while initializing, and the nodes then use the detected channels.

